title: Leo Temory Unpacks All the Drama From His Time on ‘The Challenge: USA’ | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
Johnny is joined this week by three-time ‘Amazing Race’ contestant, recently-eliminated competitor on ‘The Challenge: USA,’ and internet fire-starter Leo Temory to discuss all the drama surrounding his elimination via Hall Brawl. Leo tells the whole, unvarnished story and sneaks a few conspiracy theories in for good measure.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Leo Temory
Producer: Sasha Ashall
